  script_tag(name:"insight", value:"In autofile Audio File Library 0.3.6, there exists one memory leak vulnerability in printfileinfo, in printinfo.c, which allows an attacker to leak sensitive information via a crafted file. The printfileinfo function calls the copyrightstring function to get data, however, it dosn't use zero bytes to truncate the data.(CVE-2022-24599)");

  script_tag(name:"affected", value:"'audiofile' package(s) on Huawei EulerOS V2.0SP8.");

